XML_TEMPLATES.name: sap.chart.data.Dimension
XML_TEMPLATES.constructorDescription:
Constructor for a new ui5/data/Dimension. Accepts an object literal mSettings that defines initial property values, aggregated and associated objects as well as event handlers. See {@link sap.ui.base.ManagedObject#constructor} for a general description of the syntax of the settings object. The supported settings are:
  • Properties
    • {@link #getName name} : string
    • {@link #getLabel label} : string
    • {@link #getTextFormatter textFormatter} : function
    • {@link #getTextProperty textProperty} : string
    • {@link #getDisplayText displayText} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getRole role} : string (default: category)
In addition, all settings applicable to the base type {@link sap.ui.core.Element#constructor sap.ui.core.Element} can be used as well.
XML_TEMPLATES.helpDescription: Definition of a single dimension in a chart
